Total Students View Instructions 15

1. Create a new Worksheet
2. Name it Total Students
3. Drag _cc.CountEntireTable onto Text(Label)
4. In the Marks Card, click on Text, then the ellipses (3 dots)



5. Hit Enter to create a line



6. Type Total Students. Highlight it, make it Tableau Bold, 24 font, Bold and the darkest black(#000000)



7. Hit enter to go to the other line and insert _cc.CountEntireTable
8. Highlight  _cc.CountEntireTable, make it Tableau Bold, 24 font, Bold and white(  #ffffff )



9. Right Click and Hide the Title



10. In the Marks Card, click on Text, Alignment. Select Horizontal Automatic Center and Select Vertical Automatic Center



11. click on Entire Screen
